{"id": "art-320", "label": "Art. 320", "title": "Art. 320: Scutirea de jurământ", "slug": "art-320", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1336133624\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1277\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1336133624\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 320:\nScutirea de jur&#259;mânt </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1939995942\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1276\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1939995942\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Copiii care nu au împlinit vârsta de 14 ani &#351;i cei\ncare sunt lipsi&#355;i de discern&#259;mânt în momentul audierii,\nf&#259;r&#259; a beneficia de consiliere judiciar&#259; sau tutel&#259;\nspecial&#259;, pot fi asculta&#355;i f&#259;r&#259; jur&#259;mânt, îns&#259;\ninstan&#355;a le va atrage aten&#355;ia s&#259; spun&#259; adev&#259;rul\n&#351;i va &#355;ine seama, la aprecierea depozi&#355;iei lor, de situa&#355;ia\nlor special&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-brea